## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7ebca-187">处理<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating>事件，以提供您自己<xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>而不是让新<xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>创建。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebca-187">Handle the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> event to supply your own <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> instead of having a new <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebca-188">如果<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating>不处理事件或处理程序未提供<xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>、<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource>将创建一个根据其配置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebca-188">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> event is not handled or the handler does not provide an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource> creates one according to its configuration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebca-189">当<xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>提供给<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating>事件，同一个实例分配给`Context`的连续事件的事件对象的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebca-189">When an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> is provided to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSource.ContextCreating> event, the same instance is assigned to the `Context` property of the event object of successive events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebca-190">有关详细信息，请参阅[对象上下文生命周期管理 (EntityDataSource)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebca-190">For more information, see [Object Context Life-Cycle Management (EntityDataSource)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/67bc2486-112c-47c3-b23f-0297f7ac2160).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebca-191">有关对象上下文的详细信息，请参阅[标识解析、 状态管理和更改跟踪](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bd49311-0e72-4ea4-8355-38fe57036ba0)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebca-191">For more information about the object context, see [Identity Resolution, State Management, and Change Tracking](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bd49311-0e72-4ea4-8355-38fe57036ba0).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7ebca-192">下面的示例演示如何创建<xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext>变量来<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>对象，并将其分配给<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A>属性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebca-192">The following example shows how to create an <xref:System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext> variable of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object and assign it to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs.Context%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs> object.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public partial class _Default : System.Web.UI.Page  
    {  
        AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities objCtx =  
            new AdventureWorksModel.AdventureWorksEntities();  
  
        protected void EntityDataSource2_ContextCreating(object sender,   
            EntityDataSourceContextCreatingEventArgs e)  
        {  
            e.Context = objCtx;  
        }  
    }  
```
